{"about_the_game":"<i>A young man tries to uncover clues about his nightmares, but he soon realizes that this is a massive mistake.</i><br><strong>Play with friends in the new Halloween Multiplayer Update!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover Long Lost Secrets</h2><i>Cultus</i> is a pixelated, 2D, Horror game in which you play as a young man searching for clues to the horrors that haunt him. Roam through the location of a horrific shootout between a Cultish group and the police to finally discover what has been calling you <i>b\u0337\u034b\u030d\u035d\u0358\u034b\u034e\u032c\u0354a\u0336\u0304\u0313\u031e\u0317\u0322\u0323c\u0337\u0311\u030c\u0341\u030e\u0326\u0319\u031f\u0327k\u0334\u033f\u0318\u0359\u0328</i> there for years.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Escape While You Still Can</h2><i>Cultus</i> takes the player through a short story in which much is discovered about the horrific past of this location, and it is left up to the <i>player</i> to get out or repeat the actions of the past...<br><i>Cultus'</i> art design is entirely inspired by the artists vivid nightmares and over active imagination, bringing you, the player, an <strong>interactive</strong>, <strong>intriguing</strong>, and <strong>scary</strong> experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play With Friends!</h2>With the new <strong>Halloween Multiplayer Update</strong>, you and up to 9 other friends can play together in an attempt to find all the keys needed to escape. However, your friends may not necessarily be on your side. Up to 2 people can play as <i>The Cult</i>, who must stop <i>The Survivors</i> from finding all the keys by hunting them down. This new gamemode brings a new definition of unscripted to <strong>Cultus</strong>, and provides for fun, exciting, and entertaining moments.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Where Are You Going?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1437480/079a8226d8d954860aeabaf4b44257fb2b09e990.jpg"},{"name":"Tricky","path":"https://cd